status = "accepted"
date = "2026-04-29"
rationale = """
The positive-termination route — extending the recipe to allow coupled
state across axes or multiple live positions per axis — is genuinely
separate work, not unfinished EI-2 business. It would require new
modules, not a rerun of EI-2.
"""
